sent.orig: Assigns the "Effect" key's function to "16:9 wide screen image format"
sent.trans: 给“effect”键指定“16：9宽屏显示格式”

sent.orig: In a DAW environment, one method is to generate a dedicated delay-effect track.
sent.trans: 在DAW的环境中，完成以上的方法是生成一个专门加入DELAY-EFFECT的轨道。

sent.orig: Inductive effect, conjugation effect and hyper conjugation effect are called electronic effect.
sent.trans: 诱导效应、共轭效应和超共轭效应总称为电子效应。

sent.orig: Common adverse reaction has side effect, toxic effect, allergic effect, idiosyncratic reaction and so on.
sent.trans: 常见的药物不良反应有副作用，毒性作用，变态反应，特异质反应等。

sent.orig: The two clues embody the same expression by effect-anxiety of effect-anti-effect.
sent.trans: 二者以影响？“影响的焦虑”?反影响为共同表征，似乎走的是一条“循环”之路。
